1 the person requesting the appeal shall bear the burden of proving that
2 the project meets the applicable criteria established in sections
3 71-5829.03 and to 71-5829.06.
4 Sec. 6. Original sections 71-5829.03, 71-5830.01, 71-5836, 71-5846,
5 and 71-5865, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, are repealed.
6 Sec. 7. The following sections are outright repealed: Sections
7 71-5803.10, 71-5829.04, and 71-5829.05, Reissue Revised Statutes of
8 Nebraska.
